title: Dana Kellin Dark Silver and Gold Deco Burst Necklace
description:
Like rays of the sun, the Deco Burst necklace shimmers and shines, bringing light and radiance wherever one goes. Dana Kellin jewelry is best known for its intricate, meticulous wire-wrapping details and high quality materials.

  • Dimensions: overall length 20 in, rays 1.5 x 2 in
  • Materials: 14/20 goldfill, oxidized sterling silver chain
